The following index definition named `default` indexes all the
fields in the `movies` collection.**Dynamic:**Dynamic Mapping Example```javascript
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": true
  }
}
```**Static:**Static Mapping ExampleThe following index definition named `default` indexes the
`runtime` field only in the `movies` collection.```javascript
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": false,
    "fields": {
      "runtime": {
        "type": "number"
      }
    }
  }
}
```
